# Reef Quote (Layer 7) — RIA generator
# The sample RIA + detached signature + sample-signer.pub get committed for
# judges to download + verify. The operator's runtime private key + scratch
# working dir do NOT.
# Note: we blocklist subdirectories rather than the data/keys dirs themselves
# so .gitkeep files inside stay tracked (preserves the directory layout in
# fresh clones).
reef/control-plane/quote/data/ria/
reef/control-plane/quote/keys/*
!reef/control-plane/quote/keys/.gitkeep
reef/control-plane/quote/samples/.keys/
reef/control-plane/quote/samples/.working/
# Phase B round 1 R-1 — the committed sample-signer keypair is a DEMO-ONLY
# key that lets any auditor cloning the repo offline-verify the committed
# sample-ria.pdf. It is NOT the operator's production signer; the operator
# signer path lives at REEF_QUOTE_SIGNER_PRIV_KEY (gitignored by the *.key
# rule above). Re-allow the specific filename + the PEM-formatted public key
# next to it.
!reef/control-plane/quote/samples/sample-signer.key
!reef/control-plane/quote/samples/sample-signer.pub

# Upstream Lobster Trap clone (read-only reference, not committed; A-3 will fork into lobstertrap-reef/)
lobstertrap-upstream/
scratch/
